snippet.textDisplay:
Nobody would have guessed Brady would sign with Tampa ? Hahahaha 😂🤣 Thats because there's a lot of narrow minded so called experts trying to figure it out , and didnt have a clue . I've been saying it all of last season on this forum many times until now where Brady could end up . Pats , Jets , or Bucs made the most sense football wise , and family wise . Colts , Chargers , Raiders , 49ers , Titans , Broncos , and Dolphins were never In the mix . Brady obviously wanted an East Coast team all along .That's where his homes are .

Tampa made the most sense as I see it .Winston was basically throwing the football to the other team 30 times a season so his days were numbered . Brady is a major upgrade from Winston .Giselle is Latina so her culture is very strong in Florida. She would fit In Florida life pretty easily in Tampa near the beach , and all of that . Tampa has some pretty ritzy real estate they can move into . The Bucs are loaded with talent on both sides of the ball . The Glazer family that owns the Bucs will give Tom everything he needs to compete for a Superbowl title .Tom could be the first QB MVP , or MVP of the league , and Superbowl MVP In both conferences . Not to mention Tom's brand TB12 will go to another level with his intials " TB " matching the Buc's " TB " logo . Its like fate really .His Legacy would be untouchable if he could accomplish these things at his age . All of this Mahomes QB GOAT talk already would be over .
